<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Insert title here</title>
<link rel="stylesheet"  href="../css/public.css">
<script src="../js/jquery-3.7.1.js"></script>


<script>
$(()=>{
    $('#hid').on('click',()=>{
        let str = "";
        $('p:hidden').each(function(){
            str += $(this).text() + "<br>";
        });
        $("#result1").html(str);
    });
    
    $('#visi').on('click',function(){
    	let str = "";
    	$('p:visible').each(function(){
    		str +=$(this).text()+"<br>";
    		
    	})
    	$("result2").html(str);
    })
})
</script>

</head>
<body>
<div class="box">
    <h3></h3>
    <input type="button" value="hidden" onclick="hid" />
     <input type="button" value="visible" onclick="visi" />
    <br /><br />

    <p> 보이는 문단</p>
    <p style="visibility:hidden;">숨겨진 문단</p>
    <p style="display:none;"> 자리를 차지 하지 못한 문단 </p>
    <p style="opacity:0;"> 투명한 문단</p>

    <div id="result1"></div>
    <div id="result2"></div>
</div>
</body>
